title: A review of Episode 1184 Rosanne Barr
description:
Comedian, television star and all around interesting person. Rosanne is a real sweetheart who has had some real challenging moments in her life. She recently sent out a controversial Tweet that led to her losing her job on TV and a lot of negative press.

She came on Rogan to set the story straight and it made for a fantastic conversation.

I really enjoyed reviewing it.
